show.title: Star Moon Romance: Rejected & Reborn as Alpha
show.sharing_text: हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा
show.sharing_text_v2:
हेलो! मैंने कुकू एफएम पर इस शो को सुना और मेरे ख्‍याल से आपको भी पसंद आएगा 
https://links.kukufm.com/C5WEbS
show.description: She lost her parents, was rejected by her brother, and had her heart shattered by Asta — the one who once called her “Luna.” Branded a loser and treated like nothing more than a blood bank, she rose when the Moon Goddess awakened the Alpha within her. Star Moon Romance is a fierce tale of transformation — from rejection to redemption, and a girl’s rise to become the Alpha no one saw coming.
